This package contains a WebAssembly geometry engine compiled from original
Rust source in this directory, distributed under the Apache License 2.0
(see LICENSE).

The inside/outside sign test is a clean-room implementation of the
Generalized / Fast Winding Number, based on the published algorithms:

  Jacobson, Kavan & Sorkine-Hornung (2013) — "Robust Inside-Outside
  Segmentation using Generalized Winding Numbers"

  Barill, Dickson, Schmidt, Levin & Jacobson (2018) — "Fast Winding
  Numbers for Soups and Clouds"

  Van Oosterom & Strackee (1983) — "The Solid Angle of a Plane Triangle"

No third-party source code is included or derived; only the mathematical
formulations from these publications are implemented.
